      "value": "<p><em>Biome: Jungles</em></p><p>A tree with a twisted, gnarled grain; wands and staves made from this wood retain that pattern. The wood is commonly used for short-term wands and staves: magical items fashioned from Eldritch Whorlwood are imbued with 4 charges of the spell Darkness. [[/roll 1d4]] charges can be recovered at dawn each day. If all charges are expended, the wand or staff straightens and its magical casting ability is reduced.</p>",
